  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Xeroderma Pigmentosum (XP) is a rare skin condition that causes extreme sensitivity to the
      sun and an increased incidence of skin cancers. The purpose of this study is to find out more
      about XP patient experiences and their quality of life.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
